.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B compose\-file
Path to the compose file. If it is \(aq\-\(aq (dash), read standard input.
.TP
.B state
\(aqpresent\(aq or \(aqabsent\(aq, defaults to \(aqpresent\(aq where:
.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B present
the stack is deployed
.TP
.B absent
the stack is removed
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
